description:
After an accident, Gu Yan, a domineering president worth tens of billions, was reborn back those regretful high school days.

When he opened his eyes, the treasure girl who made him regret for life was right in front of him!

Hmm?

The same tablemate is still a fool? Let’s fool her first!

………………

One morning.

Gu Yan: “Silly girl, eat my breakfast and become mine!”

Ah? ?

Chu Youwei: “…”

Chu Youwei was stunned when she looked at the bitten cake in her hand.

I…I just ate a small piece of cake.

now I’m going to be a wife of this “bully”?>
